{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/articles/2019-03/Docker-외부-접속-허용","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"GyeongSu Han's Github Pages","author":"@micalgenus","siteUrl":"https://micalgenus.github.io"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"51226182-ccad-50b2-96d9-ea3037cc3dba","html":"<p><code class=\"language-text\">docker</code>를 사용할 때 외부 접속 및 일반 사용자계정으로 접속을 하려면 추가설정이 필요하다.</p>\n<p>해당 옵션을 사용하려면, <code class=\"language-text\">--host tcp://192.168.59.3:2376</code>와 같이 추가해야 한다.</p>\n<p>이를 <strong>CentOS</strong>기준으로 <code class=\"language-text\">/etc/sysconfig/docker-network</code>에 설정하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">cat</span> /etc/sysconfig/docker-network\n<span class=\"token comment\"># /etc/sysconfig/docker-network</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">DOCKER_NETWORK_OPTIONS</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"--host tcp://192.168.0.19:2375 --host unix:///var/run/docker.sock\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>그 후, 재시작 하고, 외부에서 접속을 하기 위해서 방화벽에 해당 포트를 추가해주면 된다.</p>","frontmatter":{"categories":["System"],"title":"Docker 외부 접속 허용","date":"Mar 12, 2019","tags":["Docker"]}}},"pageContext":{"comments":true,"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/articles/2019-03/Create-React-App-Jest-error-over-nodejs-11.11","title":"Create React App Jest error over nodejs 11.11","comments":true}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/articles/2019-03/Nodejs-import후-export하기","title":"Nodejs import후 export하기","comments":true}}}}}